# Star Wars Warfare Pack
# Republic vs CIS - Clone Wars themed total conversion
#
# AERIAL UNITS: This pack includes aerial units for both factions:
#   Republic: rep_v19_torrent (V-19 Torrent Starfighter) — units/republic_units.yaml
#   CIS:      cis_tri_fighter (Tri-Fighter)              — units/cis_units.yaml
# Both use vanilla_mapping: aerial_fighter and unit_class: AirstrikeProxy.
# Modern-era equivalent aerial units are in the warfare-airforce pack.

id: warfare-starwars
name: Star Wars - Clone Wars
version: 0.1.0
framework_version: ">=0.5.0 <1.0.0"
author: DINOForge
description: |
  A total conversion transporting DINO into the Star Wars universe during the Clone Wars. Command the clone trooper legions of the Galactic Republic against the mechanized forces of the Separatist Confederacy.

  Factions included:
  - Galactic Republic: disciplined elite clone army with Jedi commanders, strong morale, and specialized forces
  - Confederacy (CIS): mechanized swarm doctrine with rolling thunder tactics and droid legions

  Content features:
  - 26 units per side: clone troopers, arc troopers, heavy troops, vehicle crews, ARF troopers, speeder pilots, jedi knights, commandos, battle droids, super battle droids
  - 20 buildings: clone facilities, weapons factories, vehicle bays, guard towers, shield generators, command centers, supply stations, tibanna refineries, research labs, blast walls
  - 6 doctrines: elite discipline, jedi leadership, defensive formation, mechanized attrition, rolling thunder, swarm protocol
  - 1 weapon set: blasters and energy weapons
  - Clone Wars wave templates for themed campaigns

  Visual assets: placeholder - community contributions welcome. See assets/ASSET_PIPELINE.md for the
  TABS-style art guide, free CC0/CC-BY source list (Kenney.nl, PolyPizza, Sketchfab), and Unity
  2021.3 + Addressables import workflow.

  Experience the conflict between biological discipline and mechanical coordination in a galaxy far, far away.
type: total_conversion

depends_on: []
conflicts_with: []

ui_theme:
  title: "STAR WARS"
  subtitle: "Clone Wars — Republic vs Separatists"
  primary_color: "#FFE81F"
  secondary_color: "#000000"
  accent_color: "#C0392B"
  text_color: "#FFE81F"
  background_tint: "#0A0A1A"
  # EPIC-027 visual takeover — pack-relative PNG art (rasterized from assets/svg/ via scripts/art/rasterize-menu-takeover.ps1)
  logo: "assets/ui/menu_logo.png"
  background_image: "assets/ui/menu_bg.png"
  button_frame: "assets/ui/btn_normal.png"
  button_frame_hover: "assets/ui/btn_hover.png"
  # Prebuilt TMP SDF font AssetBundle (Unity 2021.3.45f1, version-locked). #965
  # Runtime TMP_FontAsset.CreateFontAsset() returns null in DINO, so the SDF
  # atlas is baked offline (scripts/game/bake-sw-menu-font.ps1) and shipped here.
  # Value = bundle path relative to the pack root; font_asset_name = TMP_FontAsset name.
  font: "assets/ui/sw_menu_font"
  font_asset_name: "SW_MenuFont SDF"
  # EPIC-027 themed loading-screen takeover (total_conversion only).
  # Paths are relative to the pack root; PNGs are rasterized from assets/svg/ui/.
  loading_screen:
    background: assets/loading/loading-bg.png
    logo: assets/loading/loading-logo.png
    accent_color: "#FFE81F"
    overlay_opacity: 1.0
    tip_rotation_seconds: 7
    tips:
      - "The Republic's clone army was grown on Kamino in just ten years."
      - "Battle droids are cheap — Clone Troopers are worth every credit."
      - "T-series tactical droids can override any droid unit on the field."
      - "AT-TE walkers anchor a Republic line — flank them with speeders."
      - "A Jedi General turns the tide: hero units rally nearby troops."

